    {
      "instruction": "<p>Preheat the oven to 240ºC/ 220ºC (fan)/ gas 9</p><p>Put a large <strong>baking paper</strong>-lined baking tray (or two) in the oven to heat up (this will stop the gözleme bottoms from going soggy!)</p><p>Combine the<strong> pizza base mix</strong>, <strong>yeast </strong>and 1 tsp <span class=\"text-danger\">[2 tsp]</span> <strong>sugar</strong> in a bowl, then add 100ml <span class=\"text-danger\">[200ml]</span> <strong>milk</strong>, 50ml<span class=\"text-danger\"> [100ml] </span><strong>warm</strong> <strong>water</strong> and a small drizzle of <strong>olive oil</strong> and give everything a good mix up with clean hands until a dough forms</p>",
